<h2>Aside 1.5.5</h2>

<p class="intro">Recording was broken in 1.5.3 and 1.5.4. This fixes it. Sorry about that.</p>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Recording works again.</b> Since 1.5.3, pressing Record failed with "The speech model failed to load: Model folder is not set." and nothing was captured. A change meant to stop the app from hanging on a slow model download also stopped it from looking for the models you already had. It knows where to find them again. Nothing to do on your side beyond this update, and your downloaded models were never touched.</li>
</ul>
